Install the JAVA Download
    use the link: https://www.java.com/en/download/
    Version 8 Update 421 (filesize: 65.85 MB)
    Once download & Run as Administrator & Install & Finish

Install the JDK Download
    use the link: https://www.oracle.com/in/java/technologies/downloads/
    Sign Up or Sign In the Oracle account.
    Java SE Development Kit 8u421: Click & Download: JDK 8 jdk-8u421-windows-x64.exe
    Once download & Run as Administrator & Install & Finish

Install the Eclipse IDE for Enterprise Java and Web Developers download
    use the link: https://www.eclipse.org/downloads/packages/
    Click for Windows: Windows x86_64 
